\title{Radon Measure}
\date{2026-03-11}
\author{boat}
\taxon{Definition}
\import{math-lib}

\p{
A \strong{Radon measure} on a [locally compact](gtop-000O) [Hausdorff space](gtop-000B) #{X} is a [Borel measure](gtop-000C) #{\mu} satisfying:
}

\ol{
\li{#{\mu(K) < \infty} for every [compact](gtop-0008) set #{K \subseteq X}.}
\li{#{\mu} is [outer regular](gtop-000D) on all [Borel sets](gtop-000L).}
\li{#{\mu} is [inner regular](gtop-000E) on all [open sets](gtop-0005).}
}
